ETH
RECTORATE
Eidgenössische
Technische Hochschule
Zürich
Ecole polytechnique fédérale de Zurich
Politecnico federale di Zurigo
Swiss Federal Institute of Technology Zurich
TO WHOM IT MAY CONCERN
This is to certify that Mr. Peter FENJVES, born on February 6, 1920, from Yugoslavia,
was enrolled as a regular full-time matriculated student at our Faculty of Agriculture
from April, 1938 to March, 1941.
Mr. Fenjves graduated on March 15, 1941, and is therefore holder of our Diploma in
Agriculture which is considered to be equivalent to a Master's Degree.
Zurich, January 8, 1999
SWISS FEDERAL INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY
ZURICH
